parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in crash situations can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the occupants of the vehicle are not provided with the necessary protection to mitigate the impact of the collision.
symptoms: Airbags fail to deploy in head-on collisions
resulting in injuries or fatalities to the occupants. The vehicle may sustain significant damage
but the airbags do not deploy.
